  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Roast the ancho chillies in the oven for 10 minutes, or until fragrant.",
    "Chop the roasted ancho chillies and set aside.",
    "In a pan, heat the coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook for 5 minutes, until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, smoked paprika, and salt. Cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the chopped ancho chillies, almonds, and pine nuts.",
    "Cook for 2 minutes, until the nuts are lightly toasted.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and lemon juice.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the amlou on toasted Moroccan bread.",
    "Enjoy as a snack or appetizer."
  ],
